# 📅 Appointment Scheduler

A simple MERN Stack-based **Appointment Scheduler** web app that allows users to sign up, log in, and manage their appointments securely.

---

## 🚀 Features

### ✅ Authentication
- Sign up and login using JWT tokens
- Secure password hashing with **bcrypt**
- Each user can manage **only their own appointments**

### 📆 Appointment Management
- Create, update, and delete appointments
- View all scheduled appointments
- Fields include:
  - Title
  - Description
  - Date & Time (ISO format)
  - Duration (minutes)
  - Optional: Location / Online link

### 🖥️ Frontend (React)
- Login page
- Dashboard for upcoming appointments
- Form to create and update appointments
- Delete appointments
- Bonus: Calendar view (with `react-calendar` or `react-big-calendar`)
- Responsive layout using Tailwind CSS

### ⚙️ Backend (Express + MongoDB)
- RESTful API structure
- Authentication routes
- Appointment CRUD endpoints
- Protected routes via middleware

